Pantsuchat is a work-in-progress group chat tool with an authentication system.

We plan on expanding this simple chat system to a full-fledged one with badges, user levels, game api integrations and much more!

If you have any ideas, please comment them or create a pull request so we can check it out. we'll gladly accept any ideas or new code :D

